'''Paul Hodge''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Hodge was inducted into the [[American Contract Bridge League]]'s Hall of Fame in 2010.<ref name="ACBL HOF">{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
 | author = 
 | publisher = ACBL
 | url = http://www.acbl.org/about/hall-of-fame/members/hodge-paul
 | date =
 | accessdate = 2016-07-31 }}</ref>

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Honors===

* ACBL Hall of Fame 2010 <ref name="ACBL HOF">{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
