===Awards===

* [[Fishbein Trophy]] (1) 1955
* [[Herman Trophy]] (2) 1954, 1956
* von Zedtwitz Award 2010 <ref>[http://www.fpabridge.org/vonzedtwitz.htm Foundation for the Preservation and Advancement of Bridge - von Zedtwitz Award]</ref>

